    .container
        h1.page-header API Project: Image Search Abstraction Layer
        .exercise
            h3 User stories:
            blockquote 
                ol
                    li I can get the image URLs, alt text and page urls for a set of images relating to a given search string..
                    li I can paginate through the responses by adding a ?offset=2 parameter to the URL.
                    li I can get a list of the most recently submitted search strings. 
            .well
                p | -- Right now it uses the Bing Image Search API from Microsoft Cogninitive Services    
                  span.glyphicon.glyphicon-exclamation-sign
                p | -- To be refactored into imgur api(no limit)     
                  span.glyphicon.glyphicon-pencil

        .solution.jumbotron
            .container-fluid
                .col-xs-12.col-md-6
                    h3 Example usage:
                    ul
                        li: a(href="./imagesearch/search/lolcats%20funny?offset=10", target="_blank")
                            code ./imagesearch/search/lolcats%20funny?offset=10
                        br
                        li: a(href="./imagesearch/search/lolcats%20funny?offset=20", target="_blank")
                            code ./imagesearch/search/lolcats%20funny?offset=20
                        br
                        li: a(href="./imagesearch/latest", target="_blank")
